lead_paragraph: As Stanford's offense sputtered in the second half, Christian McCaffrey kept urging his teammates on that the offense could be better. Then he finally took matters into his own hands and iced away another win.

headline.print_headline: McCaffrey's 2 TDs Lead No. 8 Stanford Past Kansas St. 26-13
